91
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,600
MAN: Yes,
and we wouldn't exist without her.

92
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:15,640
I'm Helmet from Picture Perfect.
I represent Gazelle.

93
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:18,320
