135
00:09:56,800 --> 00:10:00,120
<i>What do you know about</i>
<i>the Picture Perfect Modeling Agency?</i>

136
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:05,240
JERRY:<i>Let's see... apparently it's run</i>
<i>by an ex-model named Tuesday Tate.</i>

137
