I was to play the role of lion tamer.

166
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:31,600
Unfortunately, the lion tamed me.
Now I have this.

167
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,920
Why don't you tell us about
Picture Perfect

168
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,800
and how it is that you've achieved
this sudden success?

169
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:41,000
- (telephone rings)
- Tuesday speaking.

170
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,400
