183
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:33,600
(they scream)

184
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:42,520
- SAM: Clover!
- What happened to you?

185
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:46,240
Picture Perfect steals body parts!
That's how they created Gazelle!

186
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:50,320
